{"tid":2189293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來係街拎住M記外賣係咁羞恥！","createTime":"2020-09-04T19:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T01:05:54.000Z","uid":151695,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1bb7f47ee9b01bb1beff990903ede1f74ac8a1","tid":2189293,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:31:37.000Z","msg":"那夜凌晨兩點半，突然想食宵夜，於是落街買M記。<br />\n<br />\n買完行返屋企途中，聽到噴漆嘅聲，望一望，見到兩個黑衣人，全身黑色，包實左自己個樣。<br />\n<br />\n一手拎住模板，一手拎住噴漆係到噴。<br />\n<br />\n然而，我手上拎住袋M記。<br />\n<br />\n大家都係黃，<br />\n凌晨兩點半<br />\n有人落街噴文宣<br />\n有人落街買宵夜，仲要幫襯中資集團。<br />\n<br />\n當刻嘅強烈對比，我真係覺得好羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n好多野我唔知點講，我只係想講，<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">香港人，加油！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n犧牲唔係得個講字，要做到先至叫犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n比起被捕、已判監手足，你我不算甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">為我嘅港豬行為 講一聲<br />\n對唔住！</span>"},{"pid":"fb8e670e21d588e74ef5417278e72c3c46b7d670","tid":2189293,"uid":193346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:32:59.000Z","msg":"自己煮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ad1e73f109ff93d9ded6d2e08f48ab07cdeaa4","tid":2189293,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:33:20.000Z","msg":"盡力就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要同人比<br />\n<br />\n同路人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6c0045643e38157527130591cc2ea977d72dcb","tid":2189293,"uid":369920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"我連行入m記都覺得好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n你反省完就唔好再做"},{"pid":"6129d890c46c18bccdc70ce3d1c8d60d8891a4dd","tid":2189293,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"其實係好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡力就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a871cb60e7cb04f60222963f59fe08c22dcc05ac","tid":2189293,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:35:42.000Z","msg":"過左成年都感到羞恥"},{"pid":"be647f6297dd6b5994a88a79e40fcaa8c3803065","tid":2189293,"uid":262886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:37:07.000Z","msg":"記得啲種感覺<br />\n下次唔好喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2de98cc769487b1acb37522e544625f2b68e49e","tid":2189293,"uid":293344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:38:37.000Z","msg":"下次唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e12e19d5e63bcf6b7bfd7e6be802405c63035d6","tid":2189293,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6129d890c46c18bccdc70ce3d1c8d60d8891a4dd","tid":2189293,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"其實係好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡力就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T19:50:42.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好中意佢個脆香雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"